narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Compass Behavioral Health is a Community/Behavioral Health provider based in Garden City, KS. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $17.5M in Medicaid payments across 144K claims serving 0 beneficiaries.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
